Batlhaping ba re! By Mmakgabo Mapula: This exhibition shows Mmakgabo Mapula Helen Sebidi’s commitment to mythologies, ancestry and traditional and indigenous knowledge systems, through her paintings, etchings and sculptures. Details: The exhibition runs until January 24 at the Norval Foundation, 4 Steenberg Road, Steenberg Estate, Cape Town.
